    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "wait, exercise?? i dont know if i can even move right now without feeling like i'm gonna throw up. honestly i'm kinda scared to leave the house or go to the ER because it's such a hassle and i just want to relax. if i take a strong sedative or something to calm my anxiety down, do u think that would make this heavy feeling go away? i just need to sleep this off.",
